Package: maximum-pc-builder
Version: 1.0.0
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-tk
Maintainer: Matthew Chapdelaine <matthew@example.com>
Description: Maximum Performance PC Builder - Strategic RPG Game
 A click-button RPG strategy game where you build the ultimate
 high-performance Linux workstation. Features include:
 .
  * Progressive research and technology unlocking
  * Resource management with game currency
  * Strategic planning for component purchases
  * Real-world inspired PC components and specifications
  * Progress bars and city-building game mechanics
  * Save/Load game functionality
 .
 Build your path to technological supremacy!
Homepage: https://github.com/MatthewPChapdelaine/Maximum-Computer-Design-Game
